---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section class="py-lg bg-surface-container-high border-y border-outline-variant">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-md md:px-lg grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-lg">
    <div class="space-y-xs">
      <h4 class="font-headline-md text-slate-deep">Lasa Trans s.r.o.</h4>
      <p class="font-body-md opacity-70">Официальный транспортный партнер в Европе.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-xs">
      <div class="font-label-md font-bold">Юридическая информация</div>
      <div class="font-body-md text-secondary">IČO: 29587875</div>
      <div class="font-body-md text-secondary">DIČ: CZ12345678</div>
      <div class="font-body-md text-secondary">Jednatel: Aliaksei Shyrokau</div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-xs">
      <div class="font-label-md font-bold">Адрес офиса</div>
      <div class="font-body-md text-secondary">Braunerova 563/7, Libeň, 180 00 Praha 8</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="bg-slate-deep text-primary-fixed-dim pt-xl pb-lg">
  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter px-md md:px-lg max-w-container-max mx-auto py-lg"
  >
    <div class="space-y-md">
      <img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="Lasa Trans" class="h-10 w-auto brightness-0 invert" />
      <p class="font-body-md opacity-70">Надежность в каждой миле.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-label-md font-bold text-surface-white mb-lg uppercase tracking-widest">
        Услуги
      </h4>
      <ul class="space-y-md text-secondary-fixed-dim/70">
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#services">FTL перевозки</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#services">Сборные грузы</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#services">Экспресс доставка</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-label-md font-bold text-surface-white mb-lg uppercase tracking-widest">
        Информация
      </h4>
      <ul class="space-y-md text-secondary-fixed-dim/70">
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#about">О компании</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#destinations">География</a></li>
        <li><a class="hover:text-action-orange" href="#why-us">Почему мы</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="font-label-md font-bold text-surface-white mb-lg uppercase tracking-widest">
        Контакты
      </h4>
      <ul class="space-y-md text-secondary-fixed-dim/70">
        <li>Braunerova 563/7, 180 00 Praha 8</li>
        <li>+420 123 456 789</li>
        <li>lasatrans@gmail.com</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
    class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-md md:px-lg py-md border-t border-slate-muted mt-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-md"
  >
    <p class="font-label-sm opacity-50">© {year} Lasa Trans Logistics</p>
  </div>
</footer>
